getOverlapping3DAtoms

public CMLAtomSet getOverlapping3DAtoms(CMLAtomSet otherSet,
                                        CMLElement.CoordinateType type)
creates an atomSet of those atoms which have identical 3D coordinates. returns atoms in 'this', i.e. if a1 in this overlaps a2 in otherSet uses a1. If IDs in this clash with atomSet the serialization is fragile

Parameters:
otherSet - to compare to
type - whether cartesian or fractional
Returns:
referring to atoms in this which overlap with otherSet. if empty returns empty atomSet, not null
